channel.title: World of runecraft #317 Release
channel.description:
I know this will bring in much flame and i will get spam that im a leecher, but idk... I did make this
World of runecraft is a delta based 317 server. It has no overpowered items.
Download the client [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?2t1i8laa2ov0y81]here![/url] Client ip is set to 127.0.0.1. This can be changed easily in gui by searching 127.0.0.1.
Download the server [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?1xxtdhdtmf2xafh]here[/url] Yes, the file is called new winrar archive. It is because I use the norwegian version and forgot to change the name of it. sorry.
World of RuneCraft is a highly edited Delta-based server. I am spending more time on this server than my other ones (Which seem'd to be quite bad). More information comes later.
[b][u][i]Features[/i][/u][/b]
red = not started yellow = working on green = finished
[u][i][b]combat:[/b][/i][/u] Sounds Special attacks Perfected range GFX for some weps perfected magic
[b][i][u]General:[/u][/i][/b] Removal of needless customs Removal of new models for whip and greataxe
And much more. Pics show most of it.
